snippet.title: Flix Recap
snippet.description:
Welcome to Flix Recap! I'm Luke, the elusive voice behind these majestic movie recap and analysis videos.
Here on Flix we research the deeper meaning to scenes from movies you've never heard of and break them down. We analyse them and highlight the hidden gems (including easter eggs) and speculate what the director/writer/actor was attempting to achieve in any given scene. Each video takes several hours to make and involves a full production team from researchers who learn about the small nuances shown in movies, writers who describe these details and produce commentary explaining the movie of question, Our lovely main man Luke! who encaptures the tonality of the movie with his elusive voice overs and articulate description. Then finally our editors, who bring this huge collaboration together and convey the analysis we are giving with visual cues and music specifically selected for this channel. As well as on screen pointers. 

JOIN us on discord and follow luke on social media!
